\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Seb figured that maybe normal sight gets traded for aurasight. Or maybe aurasight is in everyone, in him, but he\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92d have to want it badly to get it, and no one could want a thing as bad as someone who\u8217\'92s got nothing at all, and so going blind is something of a prerequisite\hich\f1 \emdash \loch\f1 this had to be what the old witch was getting at, that Seb\u8217\'92s own lack of sight would lead to wanting aurasight all the harder. It all fit. It was only a matter of time and effort.}
