\par\plain \f1\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 Seb could have spat the spine out, but he didn\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92t want to because that would be a waste. He didn\u8217\'92t want to put it in his pocket for safekeeping because once something leaves the mouth it didn\u8217\'92t seem right putting it back in. That\u8217\'92s the one thing that separates man from beast\hich\f1 \emdash \loch\f1 if Seb ever caught someone spitting something out and putting it back in, well that person was not to be trusted. That\u8217\'92s something Gugi would do. Gugi would wolf down a roasted redtail, chew and chew, then spit it all out to pick out the bones. Then he\u8217\'92d season that pinkish-greyish mash with whatever was at hand, sometimes it was just a sprinkle of sand, and he\u8217\'92d plop it back into his mouth.}
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i0 After the winceful image of Gugi\loch\af1\hich\af1\dbch\af1\uc1\u8217\'92s most recent regurgitation passed through Seb\u8217\'92s mind, he realized that he\u8217\'92d completely forgotten about what he was trying to do: see the aura of the coming caravan. }
